1
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:19,100
♪Thinking of you,
the sky turns light blue♪

2
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:24,620
♪Thinking of you,
the sunlight feels gentle♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:28,820
♪Thinking of you, the clouds look pink♪

4
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:33,140
♪One bite, so sweet♪

5
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:40,660
♪Loving you
is like honey melting in the sun♪

6
00:00:40,900 --> 00:00:44,900
♪Even the coldest winter feels warm♪

7
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:50,780
♪Since falling for you,
I only want your company♪

8
00:00:51,060 --> 00:00:54,940
♪You see through
all my sweet little schemes♪

9
00:00:55,260 --> 00:00:57,340
♪What should I do?♪

10
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:06,100
[My Sassy Girl]

11
00:01:06,780 --> 00:01:09,100
[Episode 1]

12
00:01:09,140 --> 00:01:11,240
[Jinzhou]

13
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,240
Ladies and gentlemen,

14
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,520
eventually, the unfaithful Lin Qingqiu

15
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:16,280
was hanged with red silk satin

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,600
[Matchmaker Pavilion]
and died on the street.

17
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:21,560
[Lu Nanyi, storyteller]

18
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,480
Seeing Lin Qingqiu hanged

19
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,600
before her eyes,

20
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,560
the lady who loved him dearly

21
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,320
lost all hope.

22
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,520
For the rest of her life,

23
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,640
she never loved another.

24
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,760
Look, everyone!

25
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,800
Mr. Matchmaker is crying!

26
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,760
It's true!

27
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,720
Mr. Matchmaker has manifested himself!

28
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,000
Ms. Lu's story must have

29
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,920
moved Mr. Matchmaker to tears!

30
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,640
Mr. Matchmaker has manifested himself!

31
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,520
This story

32
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:50,080
[Love's Betrayal: Unforgiven]
is my latest work.

33
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:51,680
Ladies and gentlemen,

34
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,080
wouldn't you like a copy?

35
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:54,800
I'll buy one!

36
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,880
Quick, give me a copy!

37
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,120
Give me one!

38
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,780
I'll take one too!

39
00:01:58,780 --> 00:01:59,500
I want one too!

40
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,440
There's enough for everyone!

41
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:02,800
Don't fight!

42
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:04,920
Give me a copy.

43
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,640
Lord Lin,

44
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,600
Lu Nanyi is defaming you
in her story book again.

45
00:02:08,480 --> 00:02:09,320
One at a time!

46
00:02:09,760 --> 00:02:11,040
It's for men too!

47
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,160
Here!

48
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,840
Ms. Lu,

49
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,320
[Bao Sheng, owner of Tianyi Teahouse]
your story books

50
00:02:15,350 --> 00:02:16,400
are all about unfaithful men.

51
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,520
No man would want to read them!

52
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:20,540
- Pure nonsense!
- Who would read these?

53
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:21,740
What do you know?

54
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,200
Look,

55
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,760
there's a male fan of mine right there!

56
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:31,040
Sir,

57
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,320
[Love's Betrayal: Unforgiven]
you've got good taste.

58
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,760
So mysterious.

59
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,680
I bet he's very handsome.

60
00:02:45,820 --> 00:02:50,100
[Lin Qingqiu, prefect of Jinzhou]

61
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,040
Lin Qingqiu?

62
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,080
Lu Nanyi,

63
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,320
I finally

64
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,600
found you.

65
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:12,860
What is he doing?

66
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,540
He's touching Mr. Matchmaker!

67
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,040
Hey, stop!

68
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,880
The sacred tears

69
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,240
of Mr. Matchmaker cannot be desecrated!

70
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,280
- Stop it!
- This is outrageous!

71
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:33,800
Lu Nanyi,

72
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,680
you were the one who abandoned me.

73
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:39,800
Why do you keep
slandering me in your story book?

74
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,840
The candle flames

75
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,040
melted the red wax at the statue's eyes,

76
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,440
making it look
like Mr. Matchmaker was crying.

77
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,000
These so-called blood tears

78
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,840
were the result of Ms. Lu's scheming.

79
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,800
So it was all a lie?

80
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,120
Ms. Lu is a fraud!

81
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:00,920
Oh dear, how dare she hit him?

82
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,080
My Lord!

83
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,440
Lu Nanyi...!

84
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,180
Come and take a look!

85
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,240
Master,

86
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,000
we've been searching for her
for over a year.

87
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,040
Turns out she's in Jinzhou.

88
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,320
It's been one year,
six months, and three days.

89
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:23,480
Lu!

90
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,000
Master Lin!

91
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,240
Master Lin,

92
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,480
my Miss, Lu Nanyi,

93
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,640
asked me to deliver this letter to you.

94
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,040
[Farewell Letter]
She said

95
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,560
that she promised her life to you
in a moment of impulsiveness.

96
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,600
Now, she has come to her senses.

97
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,760
With this letter,

98
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,000
she bids farewell to you

99
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,560
and will never meet you again.

100
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,160
Master,

101
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,960
[Yue Chu, Lin Qingqiu's attendant]
the woman is heartless.

102
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,000
Why are you so fixated on her?

103
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:46,720
Let's look for her there.

104
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,360
Here.

105
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:07,080
[Tao, Lu Nanyi's attendant]

106
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,200
Lord Lin

107
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,880
is truly handsome.

108
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,000
Tao,

109
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,440
listen to me.

110
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,800
The more handsome a man is,

111
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,280
the more heartless he is.

112
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:17,760
Come on.

113
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,640
Let's go back.

114
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,440
Lu,

115
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,520
at least stay for tonight's
Lantern Festival performance.

116
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:23,560
Look,

117
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,800
it's about to start!

118
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,360
Alright.

119
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:27,920
Let's go.

120
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:32,420
[Feiyun Tower]
That's amazing!

121
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,560
Look, it's truly gorgeous.

122
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,440
Nice!

123
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,920
How stunning.

124
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,920
Lanterns are lit.

125
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,720
Dancers are twirling.

126
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:53,000
The night is ablaze with lights.

127
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,680
Lu,

128
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,160
don't you think

129
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:59,000
this is just like a scene
in your story book?

130
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,600
Except...

131
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,960
Except...

132
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,760
Amazing!

133
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,440
There's no red silk satin

134
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,720
draped down.

135
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:14,300
What's happening?

136
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:36,600
[Ji Fanghai, physician of Virtue Hall]

137
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,360
Run!

138
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,400
Isn't that Mr. Ji from Virtue Hall?

139
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,200
Quick, run!

140
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,760
It's just like what she wrote
in her story book!

141
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,000
It's her!

142
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,840
Ms. Lu is the murderer!

143
00:06:48,460 --> 00:06:50,300
[Lei Yu, head constable of Jinzhou]

144
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,520
Arrest the suspect immediately!

145
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:58,980
[Jinzhou Yamen]

146
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:03,460
[Justice and Integrity]

147
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,480
Lu,

148
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,920
I'm scared.

149
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,800
We are innocent.

150
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,720
What's to be scared of?

151
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,520
What?

152
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,960
The new prefect

153
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:16,400
is Lin Qingqiu?

154
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:16,880
According to the investigation,

155
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,880
the deceased is Mr. Ji Fanghai
from Virtue Hall.

156
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,840
His death

157
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,480
matches the one described
in your story book.

158
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,560
Now, everyone in Jinzhou
believes you are the murderer.

159
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,080
What do you

160
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:31,680
have to say to that?

161
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,840
Just because I wrote the story book,

162
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,280
does that mean I killed him?

163
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,760
Everyone in Jinzhou
has heard this story.

164
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,040
Does that mean

165
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,840
anyone could have done it?

166
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,280
That makes sense.

167
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,200
Right,

168
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,400
you've reminded me.

169
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,040
Such a sensational story book

170
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,040
should not be sold in Jinzhou anymore.

171
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,120
Lei.

172
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,000
Yes.

173
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,040
Notify all bookstores in Jinzhou:

174
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,080
Any store selling Ms. Lu's story books

175
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,480
will be fined!

176
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:00,840
Understood.

177
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:01,520
You...!

178
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,480
Lu!

179
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,920
Lin Qingqiu,

180
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,320
you are despicable!

181
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:08,480
Fine.

182
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,080
I'll leave Jinzhou tomorrow!

183
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,440
Lu Nanyi,

184
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,680
you're not going anywhere.

185
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,160
Stay at home

186
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,080
and behave yourself.

187
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,040
Until this case is solved,

188
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,680
Lu Nanyi is not allowed

189
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,120
to leave Jinzhou!

190
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,480
Court adjourned!

191
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:49,760
Justice.

192
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,720
Lord Lin

193
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,360
seems to have

194
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,680
deep feelings for this lady.

195
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,880
She is My Lord's

196
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,280
childhood sweetheart.

197
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:02,260
[Yunze Book Society]

198
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:05,060
[Notice: Ms. Lu was injured by a dog.
The store is closed until she recovers.]

199
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:10,320
What a small world.

200
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,040
I never thought

201
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,400
Lin Qingqiu would come looking for me.

202
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:15,720
Oh,

203
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,080
so he is the unfaithful man
in your story book?

204
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,520
Excuse me. Are you Ms. Lu?

205
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,360
My Master, Lin Qingqiu,

206
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,560
asked me to deliver this letter to you.

207
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,140
[Farewell Letter]

208
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:32,800
Master said

209
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,440
that he led you on

210
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,640
in youthful folly.

211
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:39,280
Our families were never a good match.

212
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,680
With this letter,
he bids farewell to you

213
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,360
and will never meet you again.

214
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,000
Alas,

215
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,400
forget it.

216
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,120
Enough.

217
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,320
I need a drink!

218
00:09:57,860 --> 00:10:00,460
[Jinzhou Yamen]

219
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,280
Master,

220
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:07,680
stop reading.

221
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,640
The villain in this story book
is named Lin Qingqiu.

222
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,800
Lu Nanyi is clearly

223
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:13,280
trying to smear you.

224
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,480
I asked you to investigate her.

225
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:17,440
What have you found?

226
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,640
The more I investigate,
the angrier I get.

227
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,880
She came to Jinzhou a year ago

228
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,240
and opened the Yunze Book Society.

229
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,560
A young wealthy merchant
has been backing her.

230
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,040
What's his name?

231
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:28,960
Oh,

232
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,040
Fu Wenyuan.

233
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:32,440
These two have made a fortune

234
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,040
from slandering you in story books.

235
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,520
Ji Fanghai's death

236
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,280
matching her story book
can't be a coincidence.

237
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,120
We need

238
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,800
to thoroughly investigate
this bookstore.

239
00:10:55,860 --> 00:11:01,420
[The 16th day of the first month
at Zi hour]

240
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:32,760
Lu,

241
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:33,760
what's wrong?

242
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,240
Another nightmare?

243
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,440
I had a nightmare again.

244
00:11:57,180 --> 00:12:00,500
[The 16th day of the first month
at Zi hour]

245
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,520
Did anyone come to my room just now?

246
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,400
I've been in the courtyard
the whole time.

247
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,920
I didn't see anyone come in.

248
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,040
What's wrong?

249
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,000
Someone tampered with my manuscript,

250
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,600
changing the time and location
of the murder.

251
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,200
Instead of stealing,

252
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:17,800
they came in to change the manuscript?

253
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:23,160
[Tianyi Teahouse]
The location's changed to Tianyi Teahouse,

254
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,320
and the time's changed
to the 16th of the first month

255
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,840
[The 16th day of the first month]
at Zi hour.

256
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,700
[at Zi hour]

257
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,080
What time is it now?

258
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,360
It's almost Zi hour.

259
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:34,960
I need to head out.

260
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:35,960
Hey,

261
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:36,800
Lu!

262
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:37,320
Hey!

263
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:37,960
Be...

264
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:38,960
Be careful!

265
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,040
Master,

266
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,960
Yunze Book Society is just ahead.

267
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:52,060
[Yunze Book Society]

268
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,520
Follow her!

269
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:56,900
[Tianyi Teahouse]

270
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:14,240
Why is this also
like the plot in my story book?

271
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,080
"That night,

272
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,320
she arrived at Tianyi Teahouse.

273
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,360
The teahouse was pitch-dark,

274
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,920
except for the flickering lights

275
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,920
on the stage.

276
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,560
An eight-chi-long vermilion coffin

277
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,120
appeared before her.

278
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:44,080
She approached the coffin,

279
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:45,920
reached out,

280
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,720
and slowly pushed open the lid."

281
00:14:10,880 --> 00:14:11,560
What are you doing?

282
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,240
You have blood on your hands!

283
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,520
I...

284
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,320
Lu Nanyi?

