Yes.

369
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,520
Arrest Fu Wenyuan
for bribing a court official.

370
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,280
Take him to the prison
to await punishment!

371
00:18:09,840 --> 00:18:10,480
Wait!

372
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:12,000
