375
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:15,240
Take him away!

376
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:17,600
My Lord.

377
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:18,840
My Lord.

378
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:20,040
My Lord!

379
00:18:21,520 --> 00:18:22,000
Lei,

380
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:25,160
