406
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:15,120
He was placed in the coffin,

407
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,240
where he bled to death.

408
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,520
I suspect

409
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,920
Bao Sheng did not die at Zi hour.

410
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:21,480
The killer

411
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,240
likely acted

412
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:24,200
before Shen hour.

413
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,360
So

414
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:28,480
Lu Nanyi is really not the murderer.

415
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,800
I've always known she's been framed.

416
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:34,080
I must find the real culprit
as soon as possible.

