447
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:04,880
Ah, yes,

448
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,400
we are.

449
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:08,760
That's me.

450
00:22:09,040 --> 00:22:09,600
Let's go.

451
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,080
