for fear of being punished.

521
00:25:02,320 --> 00:25:03,040
No matter what,

522
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:05,280
we must find

523
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,960
the person who framed me.

524
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,120
Fire!

525
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:11,520
