549
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:32,980
♪I tried to break free♪

550
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:35,780
♪No longer holding tight♪

551
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:39,140
♪Even if I returned to loneliness♪

552
00:26:40,020 --> 00:26:42,100
♪Like I'd never fallen in love♪

553
00:26:43,660 --> 00:26:46,300
♪No more new memories♪

554
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:49,620
♪No more news from you♪

555
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:52,460
♪I chose to forget♪

556
00:26:52,460 --> 00:26:55,060
♪Intentionally♪

557
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:59,460
