564
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:22,020
♪But not myself♪

565
00:27:22,580 --> 00:27:25,860
♪I think I will understand in time♪

566
00:27:26,260 --> 00:27:29,580
♪And stop relying on you♪

567
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:32,460
♪I can only draw in memory♪

568
00:27:32,460 --> 00:27:36,220
♪A version of you that loves me♪

569
00:27:36,460 --> 00:27:39,660
♪What a perfunctory farewell♪

570
00:27:39,820 --> 00:27:42,860
